This product includes software developed as the Phase 0 reference implementation
of the Agent Skill Trust Spec.

The reference implementation in warden/ is pure Python standard library and has
no third-party runtime dependencies. The Ed25519 implementation (warden/ed25519.py)
follows RFC 8032.

Trust is a signal, not a guarantee. See SECURITY.md.
